   About Me - Gladon Chua

1 / 3

Introduction

Hello! My name is Gladon Chua and I'm a professional marketer from Auckland, New Zealand. I specialize in assisting businesses increase their profit using innovative and effecient solutions. I've been working in the marketing sector for 6 years for a diverse range of organisations and clients. Through this past experience I have acquired expertise in data analysis, publication marketing, and web-based avdertising. With years of experience along with distinguished achievements and a PhD, you can rely on me for innovative marketing solutions, and with countless commissions and happy clients, lots of profit and endless experience I am the best marketer you could ever hope for.

2 / 3

Life Goals

With a professional marketer as a career, I strive to do my best and aim to achieve the highest standard. My life goals aren't just to be successful finanically or in terms of a career - I want to build a good reputation with both my career and my values and beliefs, as well as how I represent myself. I want people to remember for who I am, not what I did and how successful I was in my career. In order to achieve this, I strive to represent my core beliefs and values, which I talk about a lot. These core values are values that I was taught to represent in high school - B for being respectful, D for doing your best, S for showing integrity and C for caring for others. These values are part of me and what has lead me to become successful both in terms of my career and financially, as well as a person.

3 / 3

Hobbies

When I'm not working as a professional marketer, I work as a part-time website developer and develop websites for other people in HTML, CSS, Javascript and a few other languages. Apart from this part time job (which I consider a hobby), I love to read books. Books are something I have learned to love from young - when I was a child I read a lot more books than the average student back then. I have always loved reading both fiction and non-fiction books, but I usually prefer fiction books such as sci-fi, mystery and action.
